    "course_title": "ADVANCED COMPUTER ARCHITECTURE I",
    "description": "Processor design, computer arithmetic, pipelining, multi-operation processors, vector processors, control units, precise interrupts, main memory, cache memories, instruction set design, stack machines, busses and I/O, protection and security.  Students are strongly encouraged to have knowledge of computer architecture (e.g.,E\u00a0C\u00a0E/\u200bCOMP\u00a0SCI\u00a0\u00a0552).",
